  ; 알고리즘 분석, insertion sort, merge sort, heap sort, quick sort/ growth of function/ divide and conquer/ randomized algorithms/ medians and order statistices/ hash table/ dynamic programming/ greedy algorithms/ graph algorithms/ amortized analysis

데베설
